策。<br />\n<br />\n活動整合：<br />\n9/9 1230 大學街人鏈<br />\n每日十二點佔領大學街<br />\n每日轉堂咆哮<br />\n<br />\n公海加入連結: <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1k64H5nKHs5GVz47JvtwbWMoNe26u4bC74AQHBH-4oMM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2F1k64H5nKHs5GVz47JvtwbWMoNe26u4bC74AQHBH-4oMM%2F&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkpri3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=2138eee6\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1k64H5nKHs5GVz47JvtwbWMoNe26u4bC74AQHBH-4oMM/</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>港大人鏈</strong></span></div><br />\n間間u都有人鏈，作為(前)一大點可以冇，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>星期一9月9日12點半</strong></span>於黨鐵A2出口天橋集結，整返個joint-faculty and hall chain，夠人自動成鏈，雙線行駛至centen。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">由於呢排u-street成日漏水，當日都好極大機會落雨，手足記得當日帶備雨具準備<span style=\"color: gold;\">開遮</span>。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dfPtVxk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdfPtVxk.jpg&h=6ea9e13b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QkKQ8Sn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQkKQ8Sn.jpg&h=0bdbe722&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>佔領港大</strong></span></div><br />\n佔領係和理非必做checklist之首，我哋薄大做唔到暴大，點都執返個「和大」先。<br />\n<br />\n【佔領大學街 | Occupy University Street】<br />\n<br />\n港大人，請肩負時代賦予我們的責任。<br />\n<br />\nFull Gear、Black Bloc為記。<br />\n星期一至四，每日十二點，佔領大學街上層。<br />\n下午一點，Be Water，自由活動。<br />\n學生會將會支持所有同學的自發行動。<br />\n<br />\n不見不散。<br />\n光復香港。時代革命。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HpE2fxo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHpE2fxo.jpg&h=db25b44b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>港大鳩叫</strong></span></div><br />\n其實好多手足都話如果罷課冇活動同走堂冇分別，所以冇夢發嘅鐘數都會去上堂休息吓，但咁樣唔代表我哋嘅革命會停止。轉堂時間大學街人來人往，港大人一呼百應，只要你開口，一定有手足回返你一句，只要你開一句「光復香港」，一定有手足回你「時代革命」，身為革命之父後人，唔係少少嘢都做唔到掛。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Yw8a5M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Yw8a5M.jpg&h=c718d34e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n號外：中秋將至，有手足想9月12星期四同港大人齊賀中秋佳節，當晚暫約大家於中山廣場<span style=\"color: gold;\">觀星</span>賞月開演唱會。<br />\n公海加入連結: <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1k64H5nKHs5GVz47JvtwbWMoNe26u4bC74AQHBH-4oMM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2F1k64H5nKHs5GVz47JvtwbWMoNe26u4bC74AQHBH-4oMM%2F&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkpri3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=2138eee6\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1k64H5nKHs5GVz47JvtwbWMoNe26u4bC74AQHBH-4oMM/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T05:34:57.000Z","msg":"太空人玩唔玩得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b736856f2bb80987dd4a3c816439f5ada9999f02","tid":1551712,"uid":136809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T05:46:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fce37a23f1feb3787e8486bdb35caf7b5daa1413","tid":1551712,"uid":285915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T05:46:44.000Z","msg":"最近好似好多人話英文嘅文宣唔夠，又話鬼佬想睇到啲翻譯左嘅新聞。其實又班香港人已經做緊架啦。<br />\n（跪求幫推） 其實香港有班人好努力做翻譯<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1545086\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1545086</a><br />\n我哋網站叫<a href=\"http://guardiansofhk.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fguardiansofhk.com&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkpri3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=345f238e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://guardiansofhk.com</a>，我哋每日都會將香港嘅新聞翻譯再放上fb，tg，同埋twitter。小弟p牌冇得推po，唯有靠大家幫手推到外國人都知香港發生咩事。<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/pages/category/Community-Organization/BeWater-HK-2406628919558580\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fpages%2Fcategory%2FCommunity-Organization%2FBeWater-HK-2406628919558580&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkpri3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=7e8a353e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/pages/category/Community-Organization/BeWater-HK-2406628919558580</a><br />\n<br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/standwithhkg/?igshid=we1lffxlqh9f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fstandwithhkg%2F%3Figshid%3Dwe1lffxlqh9f&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkpri3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=a03a8ded\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/standwithhkg/?igshid=we1lffxlqh9f</a><br />\n<br />\nTwitter: <a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/bewaterhkg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2Fbewaterhkg&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkpri3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=3971c823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.com/bewaterhkg</a>"},{"pid":"3a38dcb40ed0311c013c29edd6fc21e9c84d1e2e","tid":1551712,"uid":1632,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T05:50:26.000Z","msg":"岩岩唱國歌好型"},{"pid":"05ba9ca6404cca2784460ab124ed247e8c6a65a9","tid":1551712,"uid":35572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T05:51:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4abaeb13625610383bcd6b05b0c052f52a7bd99b","tid":1551712,"uid":61806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T05:51:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b8702ee1f39620a5064ff90d74478162b9e589f","tid":1551712,"uid":49812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcf2d2627df5c25c8fae5ae778cad18e3f26cba7","tid":1551712,"uid":1632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T06:45:55.000Z","msg":"10連推 5/10"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T05:52:28.000Z","msg":"想唔想俾腦燒燈到減辣？唔想既就&hellip;<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitio